        {
            "title": "俄羅斯對烏克蘭發動大規模夜間無人機和導彈攻擊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wwIi1eNosr5D3CRzCCFOrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_2_M_1440048332.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 俄羅斯軍隊在夜間對烏克蘭發動大規模空中轟炸,部署超過660架無人機和導彈,衝突升級態勢明顯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次轟炸針對多個地區的城市基礎設施,已造成至少4人死亡、超過30人受傷。地區官員警告稱,隨著緊急救援人員在第聶伯羅市受損建築物的瓦礫中進行搜救,傷亡人數可能會進一步上升。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>基礎設施遭受持續轟炸</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">烏克蘭總統澤連斯基報告稱,持續的襲擊主要針對整夜的民用和城市基礎設施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在第聶伯羅,地方當局從一座倒塌的建築物中找到兩具屍體,人們擔心可能還有更多受害者被困。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5e5f4f2a-5dfe-3527-be62-e0a6c8098f8b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">北部的切爾尼戈夫地區也遭受重大破壞,導彈和無人機襲擊造成2人死亡、7人受傷。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據烏克蘭空軍稱,軍方在此次攻擊中攔截了580架無人機和30枚導彈。這種強度標誌著莫斯科近期發動小規模夜間攻擊模式的轉變,顯示可能回歸大規模、多方向攻擊。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>防禦和安全態勢</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球觀察人士認為,最新攻擊的規模凸顯了該地區持續的不穩定局勢,衝突已拖入第五年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基利用此次事件重申呼籲西方夥伴採取\"立即而堅定的行動\",特別要求迅速加強國內防空能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">持續的空中攻勢繼續對烏克蘭的基礎設施造成巨大壓力,為在該國營運的企業帶來更高的風險溢價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著雙方加強戰術行動,近期停火的前景仍然渺茫,使國防和物流股票成為投資者關注的焦點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%B0%8D%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%A4%9C%E9%96%93%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-094154424.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-25 17:53:11",
